videos.headline: Arizona QB Plummer takes it 43 yards to the house
videos.description: Will Plummer speeds through Utah's defense and reaches the end zone with ease for a 43-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Arizona QB Plummer takes it 43 yards to the house) 2021/11/13

videos.headline: Pledger's 15-yard strike ties things up for Utah vs. Arizona
videos.description: TJ Pledger finds a hole in Arizona's defense and rushes into the end zone to knot the score up at 14-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pledger's 15-yard strike ties things up for Utah vs. Arizona) 2021/11/13

videos.headline: Arizona turns blocked punt into TD
videos.description: Utah's Michael Williams' punt is blocked and Rhedi Short takes it to the end zone for a 3-yard Arizona touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Arizona turns blocked punt into TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pledger seals Utah's win punching in 2-yard TD
videos.description: T.J. Pledger finds his way into the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown in the final minutes of action to put Utah ahead vs. Arizona.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pledger seals Utah's win punching in 2-yard TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET
